Package org.maxicp.modeling.concrete

Class ConcreteModelProxy

java.lang.Object
org.maxicp.modeling.concrete.ConcreteModelProxy
All Implemented Interfaces:
ConcreteModel, Model, StateManaged
public class ConcreteModelProxy extends Object implements ConcreteModel
A base class for some "Layer models" that can locally override some methods but redirect everything else to a bottom layer.
